import { create } from '@storybook/theming/create';

export default create({
  base: 'dark',

  colorSecondary: '#7159c1',

  appBg: '#0b0a0d',
  appContentBg: '#16161A',
  appBorderColor: '#7159c1',

  textColor: '#fff',

  barTextColor: '#E6E6E6',
  barSelectedColor: '#ffffff',
  barBg: '#1b1a1f',

  brandTitle: 'TrabalhoComoDev',
  brandUrl: 'https://trabalhocomodev.com',
});
